{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Scorchlands</strong> is a chill yet strategic city-building game where you expand, optimize, and shape a volcanic moon at your own pace.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Why you\u2019ll love Scorchlands:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfe1 Cozy, hex-based colony-building \u2013 Place buildings and optimize your cities without stress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udd17 Deep but accessible resource management \u2013 Move resources between colonies, balance production, and create an efficient supply network.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf0d Terraforming for growth \u2013 Shape the environment to unlock new resources and opportunities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83e\udde9 Tactical puzzle-like combat \u2013 Outsmart enemies with positioning and strategy, no micromanagement needed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udd2c Tech progression that fuels creativity \u2013 Unlock new tools that let you play the way you want.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1090100/extras/Scorch_2.gif?t=1738714692\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The birdfolk of Giwi are explorers, inventors, and pioneers, and now they\u2019re taking their knowledge beyond their homeworld. Their destination? Helia - a volcanic moon full of uncharted wonders, untapped resources, and\u2026 unexpected dangers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To thrive on Helia, you\u2019ll need to establish colonies, build up production chains, and master resource logistics. Move materials between settlements, carefully balance supply and demand, and keep your industries running smoothly. All without the usual stress of city-builders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But exploration comes with risks\u2014strange creatures lurk across the landscape, and the only way to survive is through smart positioning and careful expansion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether you love relaxing city-builders, satisfying logistics puzzles, or strategic exploration, Scorchlands lets you play at your own pace. No timers, no pressure\u2014just you, your colony, and endless possibilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1090100/extras/Scorch_1.gif?t=1738714692\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Star drifter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1090100/cfbfaf0640b3d23ad8fb6faa46255de893812943.jpg"},{"name":"Speedrunner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1090100/19cc245d3e49adc85ad5031287e4009be1d323e3.jpg"},{"name":"Puzzle master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1090100/473fecfa2334fce6344fefdb4f47eecf2c868d36.jpg"},{"name":"The Dusty dunes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1090100/e09e8d77828edca522570f0f9174e211910a2120.jpg"},{"name":"The Fertile fields","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1090100/0a980a947dd85a6fefb1a3b210daa8981e1ab97c.jpg"},{"name":"The Effluvial expanse","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1090100/94bbf861cd10d0b8e1926531c672502ac90583bb.jpg"},{"name":"The Gliding glaciers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1090100/9a57e7cb9b4ff12e7280d489920af661726e24f8.jpg"},{"name":"The Tangled thicket","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1090100/9d8a717f27533d56d7e33ed0b6ccbe5e1affe76d.jpg"},{"name":"The Grand gathering","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1090100/26cd31c174f0adff441fb6beb8b6cd2784856117.jpg"},{"name":"I